{"tid":1393084,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔歸位: 罷工潮文","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:44:06.000Z","uid":74642,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12d0e45b0aa51dd6710951f12257d7d711843ed7","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:24:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，不要停止思考，所有令罷工成真嘅都要做</span><br />\n<br />\n小弟不才，剩下日子不多，請幫手推/轉載，如果有人可以整倒潮文連環圖/豆腐火腩真人版video就好<br />\n<br />\n以下正文:<br />\n<br />\n今晚，我又再一次訓唔著。<br />\n睇到一幕幕血淋淋嘅畫面，我望唔透，我唔想香港咁亂，點解香港人咁唔肯服輸？我抱住我小朋友，關上電視。<br />\n我唔知應該講咩好，作為成年人我深知道反對係無用。<br />\n<br />\n勇武抗爭？只會換嚟被捕同前途盡毀。<br />\n作為三大畢業嘅我，作為小朋友爸爸嘅我，睇到真係得啖笑。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求？喺依張國際焦點的賭枱上到底香港人知唔知道自己有幾多籌碼喺手？咁樣同我走去李嘉誠面前話要賭一千萬有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n望住天花板，喺我老婆旁邊我諗起另一個女人。今日返屋企嘅途中，收到一張傳單。係由一個弱質纖纖嘅少女手上得到，我同佢對望，點一點頭。我嘅目光無停留喺佢嘅面上，係因為我怕佢睇得出我尷尬嘅眼神。<br />\n<br />\n傳單上面寫住「5/8全民大罷工」，我有老婆，有仔女，有父母要養，重有一層樓要供。罷工？唔係我唔想支持，係我有太多責任，我放唔低，香港有邊個唔係手停口停嘅呢？<br />\n<br />\n一日又一日過去，每日平常的工作，令我好疲累，返到屋企開電視，又係一樣嘅新聞，一樣嘅結果，分別只係今日警察到底放左催淚彈，真槍定係水炮車。我合上雙眼，我問自己，乜野係啱，乜野係錯？<br />\n<br />\n終於到左5/8，我老婆照常叫我起身，換好恤衫，我望住我個仔，雙眼開始模糊。<br />\n<br />\n依一刻，我知道咩叫責任。"},{"pid":"fbe71ba35df8edec1f6020e5742475fc601ab5e4","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:24:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歡迎寫唔同持份者嘅版本</span>"},{"pid":"5e9e12a6faeec3bdf5b8710f8e53650f727d8632","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:24:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5de5d21719cfdd3dce433a1f40610b0b4ca304ef","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d8e491c2184b03f7e23a086c52bed4d65fa01c18","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:25:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d878abaed94e85eaad6225b2c135badc406280c3","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c1fbda54b278e1914ff912d4027064a0a67595fe","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:25:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3be35754342099cf1b3b66429578a4f2787bd92a","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:25:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c2747700dae0e8d851083df1d49605c58f01366a","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:25:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1f195a356ad8b39863fce99c81f32a1de561ed9f","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:26:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"41df68c24dc5c00372e573fd98e3d68edc18e748","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:26:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"da9f180a0de9fcc9e99bfce7f47ab72e2ec103d3","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:26:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"22d8bb83f7bc3cb38da97bfc912edf55348862c4","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:26:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8f4ce0c12f4792c92033ff1e07d0830464e1d62d","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"令罷課成為全城熱話"},{"pid":"50addbd29aeb42e758e4fee3c84d81a433b480ca","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:27:18.000Z","msg":"令罷工成為全城熱話"},{"pid":"309f2256144cccb1b120c3d47a63fd646452ecba","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:27:30.000Z","msg":"令罷工成為全城熱話"},{"pid":"d9c97b34004af37db848aa5694cdb2dc6d702e38","tid":1393084,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:27:42.000Z","msg":"令罷工成為全城熱話"},{"pid":"48fe